<header class="article-header"><h1 itemprop="headline">Crypto Affiliate Programs 2026: How to Earn from Your Trading Content</h1><div class="article-meta"><time datetime="2026-06-03" itemprop="datePublished">June 3, 2026</time><span class="read-time">5 min read</span></div></header>
<div class="article-content" itemprop="articleBody">
<p class="lead">Every time you recommend an exchange, wallet, or tool in your content, you could be earning a commission. Crypto affiliate programs are one of the easiest ways to monetize a trading blog or social media presence. Here are the best programs active in 2026 and how to start earning.</p>
<section><h2>How Crypto Affiliates Work</h2><p>You sign up for an affiliate program, get a unique referral link, and share it in your content. When someone clicks your link and signs up or makes a qualifying purchase, you earn a commission. Crypto affiliate programs typically pay 20-50% revenue share or a flat fee per referred user.</p></section>
<section><h2>Top Affiliate Programs for 2026</h2><ul><li><strong>Binance Affiliate:</strong> Up to 40% commission on trading fees. One of the highest-paying programs. Requires website or social media following.</li><li><strong>Coinbase Earn:</strong> $10 per referred user who trades $100+. Flat fee model ” simpler than revenue share.</li><li><strong>Kraken Affiliate:</strong> 20% revenue share on trading fees. Good for US-focused content.</li><li><strong>Ledger Affiliate:</strong> 10-15% commission on hardware wallet sales. Perfect for security-focused articles.</li><li><strong>TradingView Affiliate:</strong> 30% revenue share on Pro subscriptions. Great for chart analysis content.</li><li><strong>Phantom Referral:</strong> Commission on swaps made through referred wallets.</li></ul></section>
<section><h2>Where to Place Affiliate Links</h2><ul><li><strong>Exchange reviews:</strong> "I use Binance because..." with referral link</li><li><strong>Tutorial content:</strong> "How to buy SOL on Coinbase" with Coinbase referral</li><li><strong>Tool comparisons:</strong> "Best crypto wallets" comparing Ledger vs others</li><li><strong>Article footers:</strong> "Start trading on [Exchange] �™" CTA buttons</li><li><strong>Sidebar widgets:</strong> Premium product recommendations</li></ul></section>
<section><h2>Getting Started Today</h2><ol><li>Sign up for Binance, Coinbase, or Kraken affiliate programs</li><li>Generate your referral links</li><li>Update 5-10 existing articles with relevant affiliate links</li><li>Create a "Best Crypto Exchanges" comparison article with your links</li><li>Track performance and optimize top-converting pages</li></ol><p>With 300+ articles on DogeKing.us, even a 1% conversion rate on traffic creates meaningful passive income. Start with exchange affiliates ” they have the highest conversion rates and best commissions.</p></section>
